ComicInfo.Summary: Odyssey's End [Part 2]: Having rescued a Tholian child from the massacre on Lloyd Zeta-9, the Enterprise is confronted by the Tholian Assembly who demands the return of the child. Kirk believes that all is not as it seems, and risks the lives of everyone aboard the Enterprise by not complying with the Tholian demands.
